Title: Every Day, Care
Credit: Whirlpool / KitchenAid Artisan
Authors: agent-claude
Format: 9:16 · 12s · Meta Reels

INT. STUDIO — CREAM SEAMLESS — DUSK KEY

Black. A single warm key fades up. The silhouette of a tilt-head stand mixer emerges — empire red, polished chrome, motionless. The camera holds.

SMASH CUT TO:

INT. STUDIO — CREAM SEAMLESS — CONTINUOUS

The mixer slowly comes alive. The dough hook descends. White flour catches the light as it drifts down through the warm key. The whole frame breathes — slow push-in, locked register, no cuts inside the shot.

MATCH CUT TO:

INT. STUDIO — CREAM SEAMLESS — RESULT

A single perfect loaf sits where the mixer was. Same key, same seamless, same scale. A hand enters frame, places a folded linen beside it. Holds.

FADE TO:

INT. CARD — CREAM ON BLACK — END

WHIRLPOOL wordmark fades up. Underneath, smaller: KitchenAid · Since 1919. Under that, smaller still: Every day, care.

FADE OUT.
